Licensing map for this repository
=================================

- lib/, bench/, harness/, initramfs/, validate.sh, tla/*.tla, tla/MC*:
  MIT License (per-file SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT headers; full text
  below).

- patches/: Linux kernel patches. Each patch carries the upstream
  kernel licensing of the files it modifies (predominantly
  GPL-2.0-only / GPL-2.0-or-later, see the SPDX identifiers inside the
  patches). They are intended for submission to and merging into the
  Linux kernel and are licensed accordingly.

- README.md, tla/README.md, litmus/, bench/RESULTS.md and other
  original documentation and data: MIT License.

- tla/tla2tools.jar: bundled build of the TLA+ tools (TLC), an upstream
  project of the TLA+ Foundation, licensed under the MIT License:
  https://github.com/tlaplus/tlaplus
  Bundled build: master revision 227f61b983d0203a06db8184da45aed421e8f1b8,
  built 2026-07-15 (see the jar's META-INF/MANIFEST.MF; the jar embeds
  its upstream LICENSE). sha256:
  58d44845a37a8d776deaf8cf3a623213b59d311bc0ec287bcdfbe148dd11bb3d

